interpretation:
The anxious face with sweat is a card that represents a state of fear and unease. It signifies a feeling of worry that has taken hold, causing physical symptoms such as sweating or a racing heartbeat. This card may be a warning to pay attention to your own mental and emotional state, and to take steps to alleviate any stress or anxiety that you may be experiencing. 

Keywords associated with this card include fear, worry, stress, nervousness, and discomfort. It may also indicate a need for self-care and relaxation, as well as seeking support from loved ones or professionals if necessary. The anxious face with sweat reminds us to be mindful of our own well-being and to take steps to alleviate any negative feelings that may be affecting us.
